Defeat Orcs and Uruk-hai in Banám Lugaun

The Orc encampment of Banám Lugaun watches Minas Morgul from across the Morgulduin River. The encampment seems to be a waypoint of sorts, with Orcs coming and going: some to the city of Minas Morgul, others over the mountains towards Cirith Ungol. It is important that the Orcs at this encampment are dealt with, and swiftly.
You have defeated many of those encamped at Banám Lugaun and learned from the camp's leader that the Orcs here rally under the banner of Ugrukhôr.
Defeat many Orcs and Uruk-hai in Banám Lugaun.
An Orc camp sits between Minas Morgul and Cirith Ungol, and troops and supplies use it as they move through the treacherous terrain.
